instructions: set the plate on the tablecloth
put the dinner fork just to the left of the charger
put the dinner knife to the right of the charger
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon above the charger with its bowl pointing left
put the dessert fork under the dessert spoon with its tines pointing right
put the bread plate to the left of the dessert spoon
put the butter knife diagonally on the bread plate, with the blade up and to the left
put the water glass above the salad knife
put the napkin horizontally on the plate
